TITLE: Fixed Feedback Form with Unconditional useState (JavaScript)
DESCRIPTION: This corrected React component resolves the 'Rendered fewer hooks than expected' error by moving the `useState` Hook for `message` to the top level of the component, ensuring all Hooks are called unconditionally as per React's Rules of Hooks.
SOURCE: https://github.com/reactjs/react.dev/blob/main/src/content/learn/state-a-components-memory.md#_snippet_34

LANGUAGE: js
